# ðŸŽ¬ VistaPlay â€“ Movie Recommendation App

## ðŸ“– Overview

**VistaPlay** is an online movie streaming and recommendation app that helps users discover trending, popular, and personalized movie suggestions.  
It features a modern user interface with search, filtering, and detailed movie pages, powered by a **Firebase backend** and deployed on **Vercel**.

Built with **Next.js (React)** and styled using **Tailwind CSS**, VistaPlay ensures a responsive and optimized user experience.

---

## âœ¨ Features

- ðŸ”Ž **Movie Search & Browse:** Find movies by title, genre, or keyword.
- ðŸ“ˆ **Trending & Popular Movies:** Dynamic display of trending content.
- ðŸŽ¥ **Detailed Movie Pages:** Overview, cast, ratings, and related movies.
- â­ **Recommendations:** Suggestions based on user preferences/history.
- ðŸ” **Authentication:** User sign-up/login with Firebase Auth.
- ðŸ“‚ **Watchlist & Favorites:** Save and manage personal movie lists.
- ðŸŒ™ **Dark Mode Support:** Theme toggle for user-friendly UI.
- ðŸš€ **Fast Deployment:** Hosted on Vercel with GitHub integration.

---

## ðŸ›  Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** Next.js (React), Tailwind CSS
- **Backend/Database:** Firebase (Firestore, Authentication, Storage)
- **Deployment:** Vercel
- **API Handling:** Firebase SDK / REST API
- **Version Control:** Git + GitHub

